==English==

===Noun===
'''transmission'''
# The act of [[transmitting]] and the fact of being [[transmitted]]
# Something that is transmitted, such as a [[message]], [[picture]] or a [[disease]]; the [[sending]] of such a thing
# The [[transfer]] of [[data]] over a [[communication]]s [[channel]]
#(''biology'') The passage of a [[nerve]] [[impulse]] across [[synapse]]s
# An [[assembly]] of [[gear]]s through which [[power]] is transmitted from the [[engine]] to the [[driveshaft]] in a [[motor car]] / [[automobile]]; a [[gearbox]]
